How's your team this year ?

24
00:02:22,870 --> 00:02:25,500
We're the favorite to win
the tournament of course.

25
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:28,900
But as prestigious as Meiwa Daiichi is...

26
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:31,400
...it hasn't gotten past the 
semi-finals in the past three years.

27
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:37,210
And in the spring invitational, too, it was one of the candidates but ultimately wasn't chosen.

28
00:02:37,210 --> 00:02:38,870
That's because I wasn't there.

29
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,800
What about pitchers ?

30
00:02:41,780 --> 00:02:45,170
Including the reserves, 
we have enough pieces.

31
