The only thing is that the ace pitcher, Maruyama, is experiencing some elbow pain.

32
00:02:51,550 --> 00:02:53,390
Elbow...


33
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:55,800
He's fine.
 He's had it properly looked at.

34
00:02:57,710 --> 00:03:00,680
What was that physician's name ?

35
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,550
Doctor Uetake.

36
00:03:02,550 --> 00:03:03,450
Yeah.

37
00:03:03,450 --> 00:03:05,900
He says that it's just fatigue...

38
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:09,500
