00:13:41,450 --> 00:13:44,450
Koga Haruka

208
00:13:41,450 --> 00:13:44,450
Kunimi Hiro

209
00:13:45,110 --> 00:13:47,300
Hi. We're neighbors.

210
00:13:47,300 --> 00:13:48,290
Oh, hello.

211
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:52,680
If I'm just down by three points, I can take the lead in the second term.

212
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:53,560
Moron.

213
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:54,840
Huh ?


214
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:57,200
Haruka had a perfect
 score on one of the exams...

215
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:59,900
...but she forgot to put her name on it, so she received zero points there.


216
00:14:06,620 --> 00:14:11,200
It's like a superstar who hit a homerun but forgot to step on home plate.

217
00:14:12,380 --> 00:14:15,500
Beaten by 103 points.
It's totally a called game.

218
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:20,000
And you're down by how many points ?

219
00:14:22,510 --> 00:14:24,420
Don't dodge the question by laughing.

220
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:27,110
What are these "plate" and "called" about ?

221
00:14:27,110 --> 00:14:30,220
Those are baseball terms. 
It's proof that they love baseball.

222
00:14:30,220 --> 00:14:30,970
Oh.

223
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:32,810
See ?

224
00:14:34,100 --> 00:14:38,610
Although he doesn't do well in school, he has a baseball brain.

225
00:14:38,610 --> 00:14:39,670
He's going to be a good coach.

226
00:14:40,210 --> 00:14:40,950
Yes.



227
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:03,060
There's no one at this clinic.

228
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:04,990
What ?

229
00:15:04,990 --> 00:15:06,320
They went out of business ?

230
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:07,700
I'm not sure.

231
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:12,950
But it's been closed for a week or so, and I haven't seen anyone come in or out.

232
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:16,450
I see...

233
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,250
Uetake Clinic


234
00:15:28,980 --> 00:15:31,420
How much longer are you 
going to be holed up in there ?

235
00:15:31,420 --> 00:15:32,870
Just come out already, crappy father !

236
00:15:34,190 --> 00:15:37,750
Crap and father won't 
come out at the same time.

237
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:39,750
Crap would have to come out first.

238
00:15:40,270 --> 00:15:41,350
Get it out of there already !

239
00:15:42,510 --> 00:15:43,550
Hiro, you have a call.

240
00:15:45,550 --> 00:15:46,250
From who ?

241
00:15:46,250 --> 00:15:47,060
Hikari.

242
00:15:47,830 --> 00:15:49,150
Hikari ?

243
00:15:49,150 --> 00:15:52,130
Hey, what is it this
early in the morning ?

244
00:15:52,130 --> 00:15:54,830
Hiro, did you read the
newspaper this morning ?

245
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:57,470
I just got out of the shower.

246
00:15:57,470 --> 00:15:59,900
Read the "society" page now.

247
00:15:59,900 --> 00:16:03,660
What is it ? Did some idol get engaged to a sumo grand champion again or something ?


248
00:16:03,660 --> 00:16:04,890
Just hurry up and read it.

249
00:16:07,050 --> 00:16:08,220
Here it is.

250
00:16:10,030 --> 00:16:10,940
The "society" page ?

251
00:16:10,940 --> 00:16:11,740
Yeah.

252
00:16:14,330 --> 00:16:20,470
"Pistol robbery on the rise." "A small 
airplane crashes. Two Japanese found dead."

253
00:16:20,470 --> 00:16:21,560
No, those aren't it.

254
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:25,550
"Jail sentence for nine people,
including the company president."

255
00:16:25,550 --> 00:16:27,600
"Unlicensed doctor..."

256
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:28,490
"...arrested" ?

257
00:16:28,490 --> 00:16:29,160
That's it !

258
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:31,700
Uetake Hiroshi [58]

259
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:31,700
Unlicensed doctor arrested

